{"tid":1123122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【佔中九子案判刑】英美領事關注判決 憂損港人自由 外交部：反對外國任何干涉","createTime":"2019-04-24T09:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T13:25:10.000Z","uid":70063,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4086ada5a7a97be1ba8288aa9b85488d4cbae5b1","tid":1123122,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:37:36.000Z","msg":"佔中9人被控公眾妨擾等罪一案，今早在西九龍裁判法院判刑，當中戴耀廷、陳健民、邵家臻和黃浩銘須即時監禁8至16個月不等。多個國家和地區官方組織均就判決發表意見。<br />\n<br />\n美國駐港總領事館對判刑表示關注，憂慮判決將扼殺《基本法》之下港人所享有的權利，強調一個社會須容許自由表達不同政見，尊重居民享有言論及集會自由對香港十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n英國駐香港總領事館強調，言論結社自由受《中英聯合聲明》所保障，憂慮判決或阻嚇港人未來參與和平示威。<br />\n<br />\n台灣陸委會對判決表示遺憾，稱中共一方面宣傳「一國兩制」，一方面卻壓縮香港民主自治與自由人權空間，形容此為自曝其短，強調台灣人不會受欺瞞誆騙。<br />\n<br />\n而在北京，外交部發言人耿爽表示，香港是中國的特別行政區，香港事務全屬中國內政，中方反對任何外國干涉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190424/s00001/1556094240982/【佔中九子案判刑】英美領事關注判決-憂損港人自由-外交部-反對外國任何干涉\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190424%2Fs00001%2F1556094240982%2F%E3%80%90%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E4%B9%9D%E5%AD%90%E6%A1%88%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91%E3%80%91%E8%8B%B1%E7%BE%8E%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E5%88%A4%E6%B1%BA-%E6%86%82%E6%90%8D%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1-%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E5%B9%B2%E6%B6%89&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0p1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=9161777c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190424%2Fs00001%2F1556094240982%2F%E3%80%90%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E4%B9%9D%E5%AD%90%E6%A1%88%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91%E3%80%91%E8%8B%B1%E7%BE%8E%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E5%88%A4%E6%B1%BA-%E6%86%82%E6%90%8D%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1-%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E5%B9%B2%E6%B6%89&h=e30ac1bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190424/s00001/1556094240982/【佔中九子案判刑】英美領事關注判決-憂損港人自由-外交部-反對外國任何干涉</a>"},{"pid":"9ff6995194d2b5734b67eb52122212aef66e895f","tid":1123122,"uid":228963,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"baa7e3948819f44c98fc81f3b766fd1504a3d484","tid":1123122,"uid":70063,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">佔領華爾街果班坐幾耐</span>?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次咪算輕囉</blockquote><br />\n有個坐90日，少過今次要坐8個月或16個月。"},{"pid":"7eed10a4ed401f2576106056509f2eb0fac9dae7","tid":1123122,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:35:37.000Z","msg":"睇下有冇保外就醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04845614e01a9df0d04dc73995d00861e6fb232","tid":1123122,"uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:48:47.000Z","msg":"晚晚周果期, 邊國日屌夜屌加拿大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c863f6fbfbb93d1c9bb658f337904498103b5ab","tid":1123122,"uid":120678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:52:21.000Z","msg":"而在渥太華，外交部發言人表示，溫哥華是加拿大的領土，拘捕孟晚舟一事務全屬加拿大內政，加方反對任何外國干涉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51225b43c70be7b6bf3b8658c2494d7272899fe","tid":1123122,"uid":70063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 忌廉泡芙"}]}